title: Darby Hendrickson with PA #92Noon!
description: KFAN plays Wild Classic Games on Wednesday nights at 7pm. This week it was a 12/17/2000 game between the Wild & Dallas Stars, the first time the new MN team met the old MN team. The Wild won 6-0, and Darby Hendrickson scored twice in the victory...he joined PA to reminisce and chat hockey!
